searching.  Using energon readings, he noted the location of the other bot
on his scanner.

&quot;Here kitty kitty kitty&quot; he called out to the wounded lion.

Meanwhile...

Trelos began shooting wildly at his new opponents, narrowly missing all of
them.  Guardia continued to fire from the shuttle, which was now hovering
about 40&#39; above the ground.

As he took more damage, he started to experience energon fluctuations.
Guardia grabbed the capture gear from the shuttle and jumped down in front
of the enemy.  The trooper and Depthcharge providing covering fire.

